===Proper noun===
'''[[Fergus]] [[mac]] [[Róich]]'''

# ''(Irish mythology):'' The former king of [[Ulster]] during the events of the [[Ulster Cycle]], who was ticked out of kingship by [[Ness]], who made her 7-year-old son [[Conchobar mac Nessa]] replace him as king.  The foster father of [[Cormac Cond Longas]].